  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to Double-conversion</title>

    <para>
      The <application>Double-conversion</application> package contains a
      library that facilitates binary-to-decimal and decimal-to-binary routines
      for IEEE doubles.
    </para>

    &lfs130_checked;

